Phosphoproteomics ExpressionSet

Source: R/data.R
PHOSPHO_EXP.Rd

An object of class Biobase::ExpressionSet containing median-MAD-normalized log\(_2\)-transformed protein phosphorylation data.

Usage

PHOSPHO_EXP

Format

Object of class Biobase::ExpressionSet with 30304 features and 60 samples.

Details

RAT_TO_HUMAN_PHOSPHO for details of mapping between rat and human phosphorylation sites.

FEATURE_TO_GENE for details of feature-to-gene mapping.

See also

ExpressionSet-class, RAT_TO_HUMAN_PHOSPHO, FEATURE_TO_GENE

Examples

library(Biobase)

PHOSPHO_EXP                   # summary
